The 2018 Black Friday shopping season has officially begun, with Amazon launching its “Early Black Friday Deals”. Amazon is offering discounts on a range of goods, with sales in the Amazon devices, PC hardware, kitchen, books, healthcare, tools and DIY, smartphone, and toys categories – to list only a few. Other specials include extra credit on Amazon gift cards – buy a $50 gift card and get $15 credit – and over 50% off Audible fees. Amazon stated that it will also hold “Black Friday Deals Week” and “two days of Black Friday 2018” sales – with deals across every department. A selection of the tech deals on offer today in the early sale are show below.      